{"tid":128955,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貪曾收監：憂不慣獄中膳食　前家廚願代煲藥","createTime":"2017-02-21T08:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T10:46:24.000Z","uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5f680faa134e592f7ab91f5c39cd09f91e3286","tid":128955,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:41:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/bkn-20170220220142741-0220_00822_001.html?eventid=4028810746381ccb01465c92d00d61e4&amp;eventsection=hk_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fbkn-20170220220142741-0220_00822_001.html%3Feventid%3D4028810746381ccb01465c92d00d61e4%26eventsection%3Dhk_news&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=5d3fd60d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/bkn-20170220220142741-0220_00822_001.html?eventid=4028810746381ccb01465c92d00d61e4&amp;eventsection=hk_news</a><br />\n<br />\n現年72歲的曾蔭權淪為階下囚，在曾蔭權任財政司司長時任官邸家廚的于燕平，接受東網專訪時指，曾蔭權最終要入獄是「好淒涼」，擔心對方不習慣獄中的膳食；他又透露，曾蔭權早年每天都要飲用由中醫處方的平安茶，若懲教署許可，他不介意免費為曾蔭權煲藥。<br />\n<br />\n于燕平曾於1999至2000年任時任財政司司長曾蔭權官邸的家廚，他接受東網專訪時再次感謝東方報業集團於5年前揭發曾蔭權涉貪醜聞，又希望每名港人市民晚上回家後都能對着天空、拿着紅酒、望着月亮想一想，如果沒有司法獨立和新聞自由，香港還有沒有明天。<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權罪成後，首要習慣或是獄中的膳食，于師傅直言「一個天上、一個地下」，透露曾蔭權過去只會享用明火靚湯，山珍海味，不新鮮的食材如鱈魚等都不會進食。<br />\n<br />\n于師傅續指，自己曾參觀懲教署的設施，香港的監獄膳食是做得不錯，最起碼變壞了的食材不會給人進食，每一餐飯均有肉、菜及生果，然而「曾大人(曾蔭權)食緊冬蟲夏草、龍蝦鮑魚、魚翅海參」，擔心對方不習慣獄中膳食。<br />\n<br />\n于師傅又提及，有老中醫於十多年前為了幫助曾蔭權調理身子，特意為對方準備平安茶，自己當時每天都負責煲藥，未知懲教署會否安排人手為其每天煲藥，于師傅稱如懲教署人員不懂得煲藥，他不介意免費為曾蔭權煲藥。<br />\n<br />\n屌段片真係笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee31024ca4d79ce563d44284d809bb7ea5d634f2","tid":128955,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78416f7cfbfe6453913b7379560d1cdac7faa39d","tid":128955,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"師傅講野好生動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自由好可貴啊～！"},{"pid":"9e871782b31ad1f2d278a2ba50ded7ca361dc636","tid":128955,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"有份督完人話你以後生活好慘要習慣下<br />\n係咪貓哭老鼠的典範<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}